It is obvious that the form, entered in this abbreviated shape in the register, would be a useful memorandum for the compilation of similar documents in future. The preamble could be omitted, varied or extended to suit the case of any given monastery; while the mandate itself contains all the necessary clauses, in full or in brief, each of which could be modified to suit the circumstances ot the case.
